# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Claude Code / agent session state and worktrees (local only, not for sharing)
.claude/
# Agent orientation file: kept local for now, not published while this is a
# personal project rather than a contributor-facing one.
CLAUDE.md

# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor / misc
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# Firmware images are NOT tracked: the stock image is Line 6's copyrighted
# property and the patched image is a derivative work. They live here locally
# and are reproducible with manual/build/build_firmware.py from your own stock copy.
# Belt-and-suspenders: never track a firmware image anywhere in the repo...
*.hxf
# ...and ignore EVERYTHING under manual/firmware/ (any name/extension) except the
# README, so a stray or mis-extensioned image there can never slip in either.
# To track an image anyway (e.g. a private repo): git add -f manual/firmware/<name>
manual/firmware/*
!manual/firmware/README.md
